title: Tech rallies in eighth inning to come from behind - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech rallies in eighth inning to come from behind - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The No. 17 Texas Tech baseball team defeated New Mexico, 11-5, on Wednesday afternoon at Rip Griffin Park. On this day, the Red Raiders once again used a single inning surge as they struck for seven runs in the bottom of the eighth to overcome a 5-4 deficit to improve to 10-0 at home and 16-3 overall.
